replies.body:
Amazing what you can do when you are fed building full damage.

Here are some other champions that I've seen oneshot people with a single AA when fed:

{{champion:119}} {{champion:75}} (Q i guess but still) {{champion:107}} {{champion:67}} {{champion:51}} {{champion:120}} {{champion:202}}

CAMILLE: {{item:3074}} {{item:3078}} {{item:3156}} {{item:3742}}

She won't want to be built full tank, ideally. She will want damage with survivability.
That being said, don't color me surprised if she gets built full tank all the time.
